title: Third annual conference breaks new ground for LNG future (Government of British Columbia)
text: ( Source : Government of British Columbia ) VANCOUVER - Over 3, 000 participants took part in British Columbia 's international LNG conference this week - another promising sign the industry has a bright future in the years ahead. ' British
